Aug, you can't leave me, man.

869
01:35:35,713 --> 01:35:37,476
Yes, I can.

870
01:35:38,716 --> 01:35:40,843
Because you have to
find your parents, right?

871
01:35:41,018 --> 01:35:43,782
Yeah. My concert's starting.

872
01:35:43,954 --> 01:35:49,017
Well, all my money's on the fact
your folks won't be able to find you.

873
01:35:49,193 --> 01:35:50,524
You know why?

874
01:35:50,928 --> 01:35:52,828
Because they can't hear you.

875
01:35:53,264 --> 01:35:54,595
They're probably dead.

876
01:35:54,765 --> 01:35:56,960
